'''Brynden Tully''', popularly called '''&quot;the Blackfish&quot;''', is a recurring character in the [[Season 3|third season]]. He is played by [[Clive Russell]]. Ser Brynden Tully is a [[knight]] and a member of [[House Tully]]. He is the younger brother of Lord [[Hoster Tully]], and the uncle of [[Catelyn Stark|Catelyn]], [[Lysa Arryn|Lysa]], and [[Edmure Tully]].

